file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Basic Auth Example
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /secret:
    get:
      summary: Return secret string
      operationId: app.get_secret
      responses:
        '200':
          description: secret response
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: string
      security:
        - basic: ['secret']
components:
  securitySchemes:
    basic:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
      x-basicInfoFunc: app.basic_auth
